## MCP

`mcp.json` configures remote MCP servers for AI agents. Currently includes Linear.

### Linear MCP

- **URL**: `https://mcp.linear.app/mcp`
- **Auth**: OAuth (browser-based on first use)
- **Scope**: Issues, projects, teams, documents in the AiluraCode workspace

### Usage

- Create issues with `linear_create_issue`.
- Search issues with `linear_list_issues`.
- Update issue status with `linear_save_issue`.

### Rules

- Never put Linear issue identifiers in commit messages — link from PR description only.
- PR title uses conventional commits, not Linear identifiers.
- One issue per PR.
